Get the peak names which have identifications

Source: R/function4metIdentifyClass.R
which_has_identification.Rd

Get the peak names which have identifications. 

which_has_identification(object)

Arguments

object

A metIdentifyClass object.

Value

Peak names with identifications.

See also

The example and demo data of this function can be found https://jaspershen.github.io/metID/articles/metID.html

Author

Xiaotao Shen shenxt1990@163.com

Examples

data("annotate_result", package = "metID")
which_has_identification(annotate_result)
